{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NeF1q7RMfVEpQuXFB2GcBW","type":"tool_result","content":"12-#   Do NOT modify any code files. Only write the feedback.md file.\n13-#   \n14-#   Failures:\n15:#   - File: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA.real.txt\n16:#     Expected: 'KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA'\n17:#     Got: 'UuIw'\n18:#   - File: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS.real.txt\n19:#     Expected: 'LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS'\n20:#     Got: 'BALLS'\n21:#   - File: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Smażona zielona fasolka.real.txt\n22:#     Expected: 'Smażona zielona fasolka'\n23-#     Got: 'DLA & OSOB'\n24-#   \n25-#   Results file: tools/title-loop/docs/15-b8dddbe/results.txt\n--\n28-\n29-Written to `tools/title-loop/docs/15-b8dddbe/feedback.md`. Summary of findings:\n30-\n31:**Case 1 — KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA → `UuIw` (two bugs)**\n32:- The book breadcrumb `/ Jesien / Zupy` (Autumn / Soups) at position 0 triggers the bilingual layout detector. Since it shares no words with `KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA` at position 1, the real title is falsely classified as a \"translation candidate\" and suppressed from scoring.\n33:- After suppression, `UuIw` wins because its 4 letters escape the single-word garble filter (threshold is `<= 3`), and its 75% vowel ratio stays within bounds.\n34-\n35:**Case 2 — LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS → `BALLS` (dedup destroys merged title)**\n36:- The `capsCoalesced` logic correctly merges the 4-line title into `LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS`.\n37:- But `MAKES 25 LABANEH` (line 12) is filtered as metadata, leaving `BALLS` (line 13) as an orphaned standalone candidate. The \"shorter wins\" dedup then eliminates the correct title because `\"balls\"` is a substring of it with smaller length.\n38-\n39:**Case 3 — Smażona zielona fasolka → `DLA & OSOB` (OCR corruption defeats metadata filter)**\n40-- `DLA 4 OSÓB` (serving size) was OCR'd as `DLA & OSOB`. The metadata pattern `/^DLA\\s+\\d/i` requires a digit — `&` bypasses it.\n41:- `DLA & OSOB` then receives the ALL_CAPS bonus (+0.08). In the multi-title collapse, this bonus tips it above `Smażona zielona fasolka`, which earns no ALL_CAPS bonus.\n42-\n43-**Common themes:** OCR corruption defeating hard filters; bilingual detection misfiring on non-title position-0 lines (` / ` breadcrumbs not filtered unlike ` | `); metadata fragments polluting the candidate pool; ALL_CAPS bonus overriding correct mixed-case titles.\n44-============================================================\n--\n79-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":1,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"input_json_delta\",\"partial_json\":\"GOR\"}},\"session_id\":\"8b6ce414-ac29-443e-882f-f707c3aeef8e\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"596ebe7b-2fba-41bf-aca5-e9fc88a2fe6b\"}\n80-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":1,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"input_json_delta\",\"partial_json\":\"GONZOLA.r\"}},\"session_id\":\"8b6ce414-ac29-443e-882f-f707c3aeef8e\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"7aee5f92-547a-41ac-9fa4-4cf2660312ef\"}\n81-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":1,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"input_json_delta\",\"partial_json\":\"eal.txt\\\"}\"}},\"session_id\":\"8b6ce414-ac29-443e-882f-f707c3aeef8e\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"76f0f925-0fab-4c8d-9cc7-ea67cae8bfee\"}\n82:[Omitted long matching line]\n83-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_stop\",\"index\":1},\"session_id\":\"8b6ce414-ac29-443e-882f-f707c3aeef8e\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"3cb9dedb-4622-4298-8d07-5fece02f08f5\"}\n84-{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_start\",\"index\":2,\"content_block\":{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01657WPsgUbmA8Tm4MFxTvAG\",\"